data.description: Move into your new home in the West Oak Lane section of NW Philadelphia. Renovated from top to bottom with open floor plan, 4 Bedrooms, 1 full bath and 2 half bathrooms, living room, dining room area, and 2nd-floor hallway. Fully remodeled kitchen finished Alpine cabinets, with granite countertops and tiled backsplash, and higher-end stainless steel appliances. The second level offers4 spacious bedrooms and remodeled hallway bathroom. The fully finished basement has remodeled half bathroom, laundry with plumbing hook-ups, newly installed Heating & Cooling system, new water heater,  and storage space. New plumbing, new electrical service box, new windows, and roof.  The property is close in proximity to the Cheltenham Mall for shopping and dining, close to Lincoln Drive trail and Simon's Recreational Center for exercise and recreation, convenient access to public transportation, and close to schools.  Pictures are before new owner moved in but in still in good condition
